    <text id="B2004T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Tukey lists the books and supplies he would like to have sent for the Freedmen's
                    schools in Staunton.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Office <abbr expan="Assistant Superintendent">Asst Supt</abbr> Freedmen
                    <name type="recipient">Chaplain Manly<lb/><abbr expan="Assistant Superintendent"
                            >Asst Supt</abbr> Schools<lb/>For Freedmen Richmond <abbr
                            expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1865-10-20"><abbr expan="October">Oct</abbr> 20/65</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Chaplain</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to request that you forward to me for use of Freedmen's Schools
                    in Staunton the following Books one hundred <orig reg="copies">coppies</orig> of
                    the Green Backs fifty <orig reg="copies">coppies</orig> each of first Readers
                    &amp; Spellers twenty five mental <orig reg="Arithmetic">Arrithmetic</orig>,
                    some Alphabet cards (large size) fifty slates &amp; twenty five outline maps
                    together with anything else you may think we need. Please send these with a list
                    of prices.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am Chaplain with<lb/>much Respect your<lb/><abbr
                            expan="Obedient Servant">Obt Servt</abbr></salute>
                    <signed>F.S. Tukey<lb/><abbr expan="Assistant Superintendent">Asst Supt</abbr>
                        Freedmen</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
